              <p>-XXXXXXXXX</p>
              <br>
              <br>

              <br>
              <br>

              <!-- LEGALESE -->

              <div style="font-size: 12px;">
                <p>Please don't reply to this automatically generated email.</p>

                <p>What is this doing in my mailbox?</p>

                <p>If you do not wish to sign up for XXXXXXXX, you do not need to click through on the link above, and we will not contact you again unless you request it. As such, there is no need to unsubscribe.</p>

                <p>Thanks for trying XXXXXXXXXX!</p>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>

      </td></tr>
    </table>
    </center>
